  "remarks": "Intershipping Services Hub Private Limited is an entity based in India, as the local branch of the UAE-based entity Intershipping Service LLC. Intershipping Service LLC is operating the Gabon international flag registry, which has been flagging vessels transporting Russian crude oil or petroleum products following the beginning of Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine, including vessels controlled by Sovcomflot.",
